      "content": "thx. i'm also a bit worried about the social aspect of his care. some of the residents were mentioning that for patients like this, we gotta be careful about how we approach pain management so they don't try to exploit the system. what kind of behavioral cues or risk factors should i be looking for to assess if there's a risk of drug-seeking behavior?",
